Package header

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EDFFileHeader
    EDF file header, consists of EIAHeader and ESA header
    EIA
    EDF Identity Attributes and related information
    EIAHeader
    EIA header file in format of HashTable
    ESA
    ESA is to record attributes of a single channel contained in an EDF file.
    ESAChannel
    ESAChannel is responsible of reading and writing signal channel information from and to a file
    ESAHeader
    Records signal attributes of all channels, one by one, contained in an EDF file
    ESATemplateChannel
    ESATemplateChannel is responsible of reading and writing signal template channel information from and to a file
